Enkiroroto e dukuya

(
4  .
1  –
14  .
22  )


1  Ina pee ewal Elifas le Teman ajo:


2  “Amaa tenikishirraki oltung'ani airorie, igoro

Naa kaing'ae oidim atigirayu eitu eiro.


3  Ing'ura ituutayie lkumok,

nintagolo inkaik nemeeta engolon.


4  Ore irorei linono neitasheyie ilo orrorro

nitipika engolon inkung naashal.


5  Kake ore taata kitabaikia iyie,

nimindim ating'iria;

kimbung'a iyie nimimputukuny.


6  Amaa euriata ino Olaitoriani aime ninye empijan ino

naa enkitashoto sidai oo nkoitoi inono ninye osiligi lino?


7  “Tadamisho sii iyie, kalo ae kata ilo loo supati oidaayie?

Anaa aitiaji ae kata etudung'oyioki, lelo ooitashe too sipat?


8  Ore anaa enatoduaa, ore lelo ooun entorroni;

neun enyamali naa ninye ejung.


9  Ore te nkiyang'et e Nkai naa keidak,

ore te ndarata e ng'oro enye neijori ninche.


10  Ore ina kikurrukur o lng'atuny,

o ilo toilo lo lng'atuny pushati,

o lelo ala le lelo ng'atunyo ooti negili.


11  Ore ilo ng'atuny ogol neish

te nkaraki natala entoki nanya,

ore inkera e ng'atuny neidapashari.


12  “Aayakaki olomoni aakurraki,

neng'amu enkiok ai ina king'oming'omakinoto.


13   Tiatua indamunot naaing'uaa induaat enkewarie,

ina kata etijing'a injo naairoishi iltung'ana.


14  Nelotu shumata nanu enkuretisho sapuk olokirikiri

ina naikirikirie iloik laainei pooki.


15  Nekut enkiyang'et enkomom ai,

ore ilpapit lo sesen lai neitashe.


16  Neitashe aauno kake eitu nanu amusu eneikununo.

Etii apa enkitanyaanyukoto dukuya nkonyek aainei;

netii engira, ina pee aning oltoilo:


17  ‘Keidim oltung'ani oye ataa sinyati te dukuya Enkai?

Keidim oltung'ani ataa sinyati te dukuya Olaitobirani lenye?


18  Ore doi ninye too laisiaayiak lenyena

mepik ninye osiligi,

ore ilmalaika lenyena neikenaki enkitadiata.


19  Kebaa elus lelo oomanya inkajijik esarng'ab

laa ore olkitamanyunoto lenye netii atua enterit,

lelo oorrarri anaa olasai.


20  Ore teneitoriti entadekenya o enteipa nemuti;

neish ninche intarasi meeta hoo oloyiolo.


21  Nemuti aaya olng'obor lenye aimemuta ninche aaye,

neton ake meeta engeno nagut?’

